divs: Sighting DetailsMe, My cousin, and my mom and dad were tubing just outside of town at the hill where the double eagle 2 took of in 1976. i was at the top of the hill when a strange noise came from the sky it was a loud screatch, and a few seconds later a saucer appeard through the grey clouds it flew at about the speed an airplane would maybe a-little faster.It was disk shaped and was not lit it was probably 200-250 feet up. it flew over quite low making the buzz the whole time. it disapeard in the clouds a few seconds later.
trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Presque Isle

Summary: Saucer like moving at about speed of plane
